claim.claim-text:
9. A station for receiving a substrate carrier, comprising: 
a surface; 
three pins mounted on the surface, the three pins defining a circle having a center point, each pin having a paddle mounted thereon, the paddles being actuatable by a substrate carrier placed on the surface, each paddle being substantially planar and defining a respective plane, each paddle being mounted on the respective pin such that the plane defined by the paddle is substantially perpendicular to a line extending between the respective pin and the center point of the circle.
